 company coal mineral sands zinc and ironore date and place of birth may  9 durban kwazulunatal education matric cambridge high massachusetts us june 9 bsc computer science northeastern university boston us june 9 mba henley uk december  bcom honours in energy studies university of johannesburg  amp wharton  first job selling and packing books in a book store 9 size of first pay packet r a month first job with present group head of marketing  value of assets under your control multibillionrand value number of people under your leadership   management style participative personal best achievement being headhunted from the uk by unisys professional best achievement being part of the team that created eyesizwe coal and exxaro resources person who has had the biggest influence on your life my wife – she is normally my conscience person who has had the biggest influence on your career brian wegerle deceased former executive director of nedcor he was a great mentor and friend and made me believe in myself person you would most like to meet mahatma gandhi – he inspired and mobilised millions with such dignity and humility businessperson who has impressed you most warren buffett – he is among the great business leaders and other individuals who have not only made vast sums of money but have also had the heart to share this blessing with others philosophy of life give share love and make the world a better place biggest ever opportunity eyesizwe coal biggest ever disappointment before i thought a previous failed business venture was in later life i realised that i learned lifechanging lessons during that experience hope for the future global respect for south africa and poverty alleviation favourite reading spiritual selfimprovement and business books favourite tv programme history channel favourite fooddrink universal food tastewater favourite music classical and jazz favourite sport none hobbies listening to music and reading – i try to go to the gym four times a week and recently started horse riding car isuzu bakkie pets none miscellaneous dislikes corruption favourite other south african company african rainbow minerals i admire what the company has achieved in the past ten years sasol is a close second favourite foreign company bhp billiton married thandeka nyembezi january  9 children malwande  vuyokazi  clubs none edited by martin zhuwakinyucreamer media senior deputy editor email this article      save this article to subscribe email subscriptionscreamermediacoza or click here to advertise email advertisingcreamermediacoza or click here comment guidelines rss feed about mining weekly is a product of creamer mediawwwcreamermediacoza other creamer media products includeengineering newsresearch channel africapolity read more about newsletters sign up for our free daily email newsletter receive daily sector news alerts more newsletters subscriptions we offer a variety of subscriptions to our magazine website pdf reports and our photo library subscriptions are available via the creamer media store view store subscriptions advertise advertising on miningweeklycom is an effective way to build and consolidate a companys profile among clients and prospective clients email advertisingcreamermediacoza view options advertise subscribe read now advertise now sq s  pq  rq legal notice comment guidelines  copyright  close